{"tid":2413138,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"北角現變態狂徒推3名OL出馬路 一人撞斷牙手指脫臼","createTime":"2021-02-18T12:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T14:52:55.000Z","uid":117934,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0aafa769a223b261ab019043ce42ac78da41dd97","tid":2413138,"uid":117934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:57:43.000Z","msg":"北角年初五出現變態狂徒，將3名女子推出馬路致受傷送院。周二（16日）下午3時許，3名女子（26至38歲）於七姊妹道與健康西街交界等過馬路時，突然被一名陌生男子從後推出馬路，原因不明。3人跌倒在地上，口、手及腳部受傷流血，事後到東區醫院求醫，案件列作襲擊致造成身體傷害，現交由東區警區刑事調查隊第5隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/F0pM03pFaV7rmmdPZ7InLqwOorY=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KNXBKGW4VJEW5KZDSCWRCQKBWU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FF0pM03pFaV7rmmdPZ7InLqwOorY%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKNXBKGW4VJEW5KZDSCWRCQKBWU.JPG&h=f6c52e13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210217/RVWTNC7FABEATDXXHMQ35Q3QFU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1NZ12532RrFPsbTBW4v73ZBBxzTMG4PkvYhJjwT1B7vHS7eSr1Zxc5Reo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210217%2FRVWTNC7FABEATDXXHMQ35Q3QFU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1NZ12532RrFPsbTBW4v73ZBBxzTMG4PkvYhJjwT1B7vHS7eSr1Zxc5Reo&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69BdyOQTk4RMct2Rsqyof94c%3D&h=5e4948ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210217%2FRVWTNC7FABEATDXXHMQ35Q3QFU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1NZ12532RrFPsbTBW4v73ZBBxzTMG4PkvYhJjwT1B7vHS7eSr1Zxc5Reo&h=cbe8f8b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210217/RVWTNC7FABEATDXXHMQ35Q3QFU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1NZ12532RrFPsbTBW4v73ZBBxzTMG4PkvYhJjwT1B7vHS7eSr1Zxc5Reo</a><br />\n<br />\n消息指，3人於北角一間公司從事文職工作，為同事關係，她們於健威坊食完午飯後，沿七姊妹道返回公司，其間在行人過路處等過馬路時，突然被一名身高約1.7米高、年約30多歲的陌生男子從後推出馬路，並跌倒在地上。涉案男子其後拔足狂奔，逃之夭夭。據知，其中一名女子傷勢較重，一隻牙被撞斷、2隻牙移位、一隻手指脫臼，需要留院治理，事後她們向警方報稱未有與人結怨，亦未見過涉案男子，所以未知該男子的動機及企圖。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，3名OL的公司今日（17日）發出通告，提醒員工外出時要注意安全，避免站近馬路邊，並指生命攸關，請加倍小心，格外留神。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SkCZCzulmXQeOhH0b-M_Lz-5nVU=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/27EOKMOJRNBWBHD7S7QMBWIW6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSkCZCzulmXQeOhH0b-M_Lz-5nVU%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F27EOKMOJRNBWBHD7S7QMBWIW6E.jpg&h=41b99a30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><br />\nCHING SICK BALL</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"92ae392042488429bf71917ea6b6cfcd546cd7b4","tid":2413138,"uid":117934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:11:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c12be5baaf3cdd992daa0f663e57f8324b850f1a","tid":2413138,"uid":117934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:11:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5be99b544c4943fb577264b01fab6c60d13a61b9","tid":2413138,"uid":373567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6HC3Wt1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6HC3Wt1.png&h=d52ce514&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3da624f757b678cfa479ee92830e0d5b60982f34","tid":2413138,"uid":67302,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"